        <div id="intro1" class="intro1"> <img src="images/tna-centenary-map-cyprus.png" title="Cyprus" alt="Small outline image of Cyprus" class="float-right" />
          <p>The location of Cyprus at the eastern end of the Mediterranean meant that it was strategically and diplomatically important within the campaigns against the Ottoman Empire. The island saw no military action but was at the centre of diplomatic efforts to bring Greece into the conflict. Cyprus was also an important base for intelligence and counter-intelligence operations.</p>
          
        </div>
